<h2 id="applications">Applications</h2>
<p>We decided to work on what we believed to be 6 most important applications, Home, Email, Search, News, Word Processor, and File Manager.</p>

<h3 id="home">Home:</h3>
<p>In order to ensure simplicity in this project, we decided to make the home screen as minimal as possible. Inspired by iOS and Android, this is a grid layout, showing all of your applications on the same screen.</p>

